theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
text = "Hello!

This game doesn't have any goal or a proper game design. It is about chilling and playing bowling for fun.

You can customize walls with your own favorite images by interacting with the poster placeholders.

To move you can use WASD keys and mouse for camera rotation. 

To grab a ball or interact with something you can use E key. 

For throwing a bowling ball you have to hold left mouse button and release it after you get enough power. 

ESC - for menu

Be cool dudes!"
